Description_lang: Your empower spells' maximum level is increased by 1, and they reach maximum empower level $s3% faster.

description_blz.en_US: Your empower spells' maximum level is increased by 1, and they reach maximum empower level 20% faster.

description_blz.ko_KR: 강화 주문의 최대 단계가 1만큼 증가합니다. 또한 최대 강화 단계에 도달하는 속도가 20%만큼 빨라집니다.
